### Our Story
Founded in 2006 by Dr. Konstantinos A. Vlachos and later joined by Dr. Elena M. Karras, Aesthetikon was born from a desire to create a different kind of plastic surgery experience in Greece — one that combined the highest international standards with genuine human warmth and discretion.

What began as a small practice has grown into Thessaloniki’s most respected name in aesthetic surgery, attracting patients from across Greece and abroad who seek results that feel authentic, not artificial.

