### 1. Deep Plane Facelift & Neck Lift
**Tagline:** The gold standard in facial rejuvenation.

**Description:**  
The deep plane facelift is the most advanced technique for restoring youthful facial contours. Unlike traditional facelifts that only tighten skin, the deep plane approach repositions the underlying SMAS layer and facial ligaments, creating results that look natural and last significantly longer — typically 10–15 years.

**Ideal For:**  
Patients in their late 40s to early 70s experiencing significant sagging of the midface, jowls, and neck.

**What Makes Us Different:**  
Dr. Karras performs an extended deep plane technique with selective fat grafting and platysma muscle tightening. The result is a refreshed, never “pulled” appearance.

**Recovery:**  
Most patients return to social activities in 10–14 days. Final results continue to refine over 6–12 months.

**Duration:** 4–6 hours under general anesthesia  
**Hospital Stay:** 1 night  
**Scars:** Hidden within the hairline and natural creases

---

### 2. Rhinoplasty (Primary & Revision)
**Tagline:** Refining the nose while preserving identity.

**Description:**  
Whether you seek subtle refinement or correction of functional issues, our rhinoplasty approach prioritizes harmony with your unique facial features and ethnic background. We never apply a “one nose fits all” philosophy.

**Techniques Offered:**
- Open and closed rhinoplasty
- Preservation rhinoplasty (dorsal preservation)
- Ultrasonic (piezo) rhinoplasty for precision
- Revision rhinoplasty (specialty)

**Ideal For:**  
Patients unhappy with the size, shape, or function of their nose, or those seeking correction after previous surgery.

**Recovery:**  
7–10 days of visible swelling/bruising. Subtle refinement continues for 12–18 months.

---

### 3. Breast Augmentation
**Tagline:** Proportion. Softness. Confidence.

**Description:**  
We offer both implant-based and fat-transfer breast augmentation. Every augmentation is planned using 3D imaging and detailed measurements to achieve results that feel like a natural extension of your body.

**Options:**
- Motiva, Mentor, and Allergan implants (round and anatomical)
- Subfascial, submuscular, and dual-plane placement
- Composite augmentation (implant + fat grafting)
- Fat-only transfer for modest enhancement

**Recovery:**  
Most patients return to desk work in 5–7 days. Full exercise in 6 weeks.

---

### 4. Liposculpture & High-Definition Body Contouring
**Tagline:** Sculpting with precision, not just removal.

**Description:**  
Using advanced VASER and power-assisted techniques, we remove and strategically reposition fat to reveal your underlying anatomy. This is not weight-loss surgery — it is artistic body sculpting.

**Popular Areas:**
- Abdomen and waist (creating an athletic “V”)
- Flanks and love handles
- Inner and outer thighs
- Arms and back
- Chin and neck

**Recovery:**  
Compression garments for 4–6 weeks. Most swelling resolves in 6–8 weeks. Final results at 3–6 months.

---

### 5. Blepharoplasty (Upper & Lower Eyelids)
**Tagline:** Open the eyes. Refresh the face.

**Description:**  
Eyelid surgery is one of the highest-impact, lowest-downtime procedures we offer. We remove excess skin and reposition or remove fat to eliminate puffiness and hooded lids while preserving a natural, expressive appearance.

**Techniques:**
- Upper blepharoplasty
- Lower blepharoplasty (transconjunctival or skin approach)
- Canthopexy for support
- Fat repositioning instead of removal

**Recovery:**  
5–7 days of visible bruising. Makeup can usually be worn after 7–10 days.

---

### 6. Abdominoplasty (Tummy Tuck)
**Tagline:** Restoring the abdomen after life’s changes.

**Description:**  
We offer full, mini, and extended abdominoplasty techniques, often combined with liposuction (lipoabdominoplasty) and muscle repair (diastasis recti correction).

**Ideal For:**  
Women after pregnancy and individuals after significant weight loss.

**Recovery:**  
2 weeks off work (desk job). Full recovery 6–8 weeks. Final scar maturation 12–18 months.

---

### 7. Mommy Makeover
**Tagline:** Reclaiming your body after motherhood.

**Description:**  
A customized combination of procedures — typically breast surgery, tummy tuck, and liposuction — designed to restore your pre-pregnancy figure in a single, carefully planned surgical journey.

**Recovery:**  
Most patients need 2–3 weeks of significant downtime. Full return to normal activities in 6–8 weeks.

---

### 8. Non-Surgical Facial Rejuvenation
**Tagline:** Graceful aging, without surgery.

**Treatments:**
- Advanced Botox and dermal fillers (natural approach)
- Profhilo and skin boosters
- Morpheus8 radiofrequency microneedling
- CO2 and fractional laser resurfacing
- Thread lifts (for mild laxity)
- Medical-grade skincare protocols

**Philosophy:** We use injectables conservatively to enhance, never to freeze or distort.

